OL,3,CUkrainian refugee family on building a
OL,4,Cnew life in Somerset
OL,6,FA Ukrainian man who found a new life
OL,7,Fand career in Somerset wants more
OL,8,Fpeople to understand the positive
OL,9,Fimpact refugees can bring to society.
OL,11,FWhen Russia began its full-scale
OL,12,Finvasion of Ukraine in 2022, tech
OL,13,Fentrepreneur, Alex Pervak, and
OL,14,Fjournalist, Kateryna Luchyna, were
OL,15,Fliving in Kyiv with their two young
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,F"My biggest fear was being under
OL,19,Foccupation. It's the most scary thing
OL,20,Fin the world," Kateryna told ITV News.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
