OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781784675
OL,3,CUkrainian refugee family on building a
OL,4,Cnew life in Somerset
OL,6,FAs the conflict escalated in war torn
OL,7,FUkraine, the family sought sanctuary
OL,8,Fin the UK and eventually found a host
OL,9,Fin Somerset.
OL,11,FAlex says that from the get-go they
OL,12,Freceived a warm welcome from the local
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,FHowever, despite decades of
OL,16,Fprofessional experience in his native
OL,17,Fcountry, Alex struggled to secure a
OL,18,Fjob.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
