OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781784675
OL,3,CUkrainian refugee family on building a
OL,4,Cnew life in Somerset
OL,6,FLast year, he started working with
OL,7,Fsocial enterprise EqualReach, which
OL,8,Fhelped him find a new role at Amazon.
OL,10,FThe family had to register for
OL,11,FUniversal Credit before Alex found the
OL,12,Frole.
OL,14,F"It feels that you're no longer taking
OL,15,Fbut bringing something - it feels good
OL,16,Fto be a useful part of society," says
OL,17,FKateryna.
OL,19,FAlex told ITV News: "I feel that I
OL,20,Fbring value because my previous
OL,21,Fexperience works in a much better way".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
