CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781784675
OL,3,CUkrainian refugee family on building a
OL,4,Cnew life in Somerset
OL,6,FGiselle Gonzales is the founder of
OL,7,FEqualReach and says refugees' talent
OL,8,Fcan often go overlooked.
OL,10,FShe said: "The call to action for
OL,11,Fbusinesses is to make sure that this
OL,12,Ftalent does not go overlooked. That
OL,13,Fcall to action to business leaders is
OL,14,Fto give work, not aid, because aid
OL,15,Fresponds to crisis, but work rebuilds
OL,16,Fthe future."
OL,18,FThe business founder continued:
OL,19,F"Alex's story is such a beautiful
OL,20,Fexample of someone who has come to
OL,21,Fthis country with resilience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781784675
OL,3,CUkrainian refugee family on building a
OL,4,Cnew life in Somerset
OL,6,F"They've taken a situation that I
OL,7,Fwouldn't wish on anyone and they've
OL,8,Fturned it around to not only rebuild
OL,9,Ftheir own lives, help their family
OL,10,Fsettle, but also to represent what
OL,11,Frefugee communities can bring to their
OL,12,Flocal community."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
